"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The hackers made away with a mix of over 20 tokens that includes altcoins such as BNB, Safemoon, BSC-USD and BPay.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/S45sp0fsmizqBAv5FjiEM.png?height=955&width=1434)\\n\\nCrypto exchange Bitmart lost nearly $200 million in a hot wallet compromise hosted over the Ethereum and Binance Smart Chain blockchains.\\n\\nThe $200 million Bitmart hack was first revealed by Peckshield, a blockchain security and data analytics company that initially [identified](https://etherscan.io/tokentxns?a=0x39fb0dcd13945b835d47410ae0de7181d3edf270%27) a transfer of roughly $100 million over the Ethereum blockchain.\\n\\nFurther investigation from the team revealed a concurrent hack of $96 million over the crypto exchange’s BSC reserves:\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/peckshield/status/1467310381073047552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1467310381073047552%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Fbitmart-hacked-for-200m-following-ethereum-binance-smart-chain-exploit](https://twitter.com/peckshield/status/1467310381073047552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1467310381073047552%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Fbitmart-hacked-for-200m-following-ethereum-binance-smart-chain-exploit)\\n\\nThe hackers made away with a mix of over 20 tokens that includes altcoins such as Binance Coin ([BNB](https://cointelegraph.com/binance-coin-price-index)), Safemoon, BSC-USD and BNBBPay (BPay). Sizable amounts of meme coins such as BabyDoge, Floki and Moonshot were also compromised in the hack. \\n\\n[According](https://twitter.com/peckshield/status/1467318513971118083) to Peckshield, the hack was a straightforward case of transfer-out, swap, and wash:\\n\\n![Transfer of stolen tokens on Bitmart. Source: PeckShield](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1_w5YShEyUw8U2AhezvJ0.png?height=594&width=1838)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/sheldonbitmart/status/1467316365732233219?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1467316365732233219%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Fbitmart-hacked-for-200m-following-ethereum-binance-smart-chain-exploit](https://twitter.com/sheldonbitmart/status/1467316365732233219?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1467316365732233219%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Fbitmart-hacked-for-200m-following-ethereum-binance-smart-chain-exploit)\\n\\nBitmart CEO Sheldon Xia later confirmed the hack over Twitter as a “large-scale security breach” on ETH and BSC hot wallets:\\n\\n> “At this moment we are still concluding the possible methods used. The hackers were able to withdraw assets of the value of approximately USD 150 million.”\\n>\\n> **Related: *[Crypto lending firm Celsius reportedly affected in BadgerDAO exploit](https://cointelegraph.com/news/crypto-lending-firm-celsius-reportedly-affected-in-badgerdao-exploit)***\\n>\\n> In what seems like an ongoing threat to the crypto ecosystem, cryptocurrency lending platform Celsius confirmed [a loss of $50 million](https://cointelegraph.com/news/badgerdao-reportedly-suffers-security-breach-and-loses-10m) in the exploit of decentralized finance (DeFi) protocol BadgerDAO.\\n>\\n> The first reports on BadgerDAO’s security breach surfaced on Thursday with the protocol officially announcing that it received multiple exports of unauthorized withdrawals of user funds on Wednesday.\\n>\\n> Taking preventive measures similar to Bitmart, the Badger team continued investigating the issue and paused all smart contracts on the protocol to avoid any further losses.\",\"timestamp\":1639639108,\"title\":\"Bitmart hacked for $200M following Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain exploit\"},\"digest\":\"PcEJmg3bA1SFTvNeryF26T0rHYarv9NIUVoaD_DzTGM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x56ae078aBf20a62158f5E0B277b9a0dF0A76e4E9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"VS70R98Pe6Geb6NmG-PCyg4vfEriTE_x7M7boh-OhEc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Syoe1pu4UBFZiUbGGeIbDaJpIGa-Egtwv_nYP9dwAhI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"eD8u0gjyhXIuztkd6grX-z8aRQl6FNhjZtxu--MhilOoWhgkHgJ0cF0sH681UZJd0mpkSAok2RH8Zgxpx-R33g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xee8b710905f87c2e1b451d0d041739f5152baf83f79fe90f142f12088bc27a955147960e993c45155e2718f377a02b5384adc39c0d1eab60c6f5758a60de36471b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"VS70R98Pe6Geb6NmG-PCyg4vfEriTE_x7M7boh-OhEc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Syoe1pu4UBFZiUbGGeIbDaJpIGa-Egtwv_nYP9dwAhI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"PcEJmg3bA1SFTvNeryF26T0rHYarv9NIUVoaD_DzTGM\"}"